            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-01/jiuyuan.jpg?VersionId=qbdLeN3chmWvf0QtZBpZeil5Lm5_m.aB&itok=5vLNz9f0" title="重庆市武隆区一单位食堂垮塌，20余人被困，消防员到场救援。（互联网）" alt="重庆市武隆区一单位食堂垮塌，20余人被困，消防员到场救援。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-01/jiuyuan.jpg?VersionId=qbdLeN3chmWvf0QtZBpZeil5Lm5_m.aB&itok=5vLNz9f0" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
